### 강의 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/lectures

### 강의 등록
POST http://localhost:8080/lectures
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Python",
  "price": 20000
}

### 강의 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/lectures
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Kotlin",
  "price": 20000
}

### 강의 삭제
DELETE http://localhost:8080/lectures?id=1

### 홈 (JSP 렌더 확인)
GET http://localhost:8080/